# Caveman-Skeltons

This includes skeltons for [Caveman2](https://github.com/fukamachi/caveman).

***Note: The base skelton (in the master branch) is copied from the original skelton in caveman2.***

## Instalation & Usage

At first, checkout a branch that contains a skelton that you hope to use.

```lisp
;; omit output
> (ql:quickload :caveman-skeltons)
> (caveman-skeltons:make-project #p"/path/to/project")
```

